\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:41.5px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f9/Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg/120px-Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg\" width=\"120\" height=\"67\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f9/Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg/180px-Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f9/Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg/240px-Collared_in_early_rugby_union.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1796\" data-file-height=\"1008\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>Rugby union match\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Stanley_Berkeley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Harrington, Peter (1993). <i>British Artists and War: The Face of Battle in Paintings and Prints, 1700-1914.</i> London: Greenhill.</li>\n<li>Mortimer, R., \"A Battle-Painter at Home: Mr. Stanley Berkeley and his Work,\" <i><a href=\"/wiki/Windsor_Magazine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Windsor Magazine\">Windsor Magazine</a></i>, Vol. X, July 1899, pp.&#160;123\u2013132.</li>\n<li>Obituary, <i>The Times</i>, April 24, 1909, page 15.</li></ul>\n<table role=\"presentation\" class=\"mbox-small plainlinks sistersitebox\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;color:#000\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"mbox-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/30px-Commons-logo.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"40\" class=\"noviewer\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/45px-Co